translations.name: notice
translations.content: The marina is located in the city centre adjacent to the Cork Customs House building on Custom House Quay which was completed in 1819 and became the Headquarters of the Port Company. From arrival in the Port, visitors will be immersed in Cork’s maritime heritage that integrates history including the home of the Oldest Yacht Club in the World, founded in 1720. Cork’s story is anchored in one of the world’s greatest natural harbours and stretches around the globe. The Coat of Arms of the Port is “Statio Bene Fida Carinis” (Safe Harbour for Ships). A visit to Cork Harbour opens up to visitors a number of impressive heritage sites associated with Cork’s Maritime Heritage and are accessible by visiting boats.

Du skal kun bruge et klistermærke i alle havne, der bruger Harba, det er gratis og kræves i visse havne. translations.name: notice
translations.content:
Korshavn Lystbådebro is located by Fyns Hoved - one of the most beautiful places in Denmark - and is owned by Odense sailing club.
At the bridge you will find electricity and water as well as the opportunity to get rid of your waste. Public toilets - without shower -are just 250 meters away from the bridge. The surroundings are incredibly picturesque with high slopes, shallow areas and a breathtaking view of Æbelø, Jutland, Samsø and Zealand.
The surroundings are perfect for taking a walk, hiking or just relaxing by the beach with a good book. For more information, press i.

translations.name: notice
translations.content:
Korshavn Lystbådebro is located by Fyns Hoved - one of the most beautiful places in Denmark - and is owned by Odense sailing club.
At the bridge you will find electricity and water as well as the opportunity to get rid of your waste. Public toilets are just 250 meters away from the bridge. The surroundings are incredibly picturesque with high slopes, shallow areas and a breathtaking view of Æbelø, Jutland, Samsø and Zealand.
The surroundings are perfect for taking a walk, hiking or just relaxing by the beach with a good book. For more information, press i.

translations.name: notice
translations.content:
Korshavn Lystbådebro ligger ved Fyns Hoved – et af de smukkeste steder i Danmark – og er ejet af Odense sejlklub.
Ved broen finder du EL og vand samt muligheden for at komme af med dit affald. Offentlige toiletter - uden badefacilitet - findes blot 250 meter væk fra broen. Omgivelserne er utroligt maleriske med høje skråninger, lavvandet områder og en betagende udsigt over Æbelø, Jylland, Samsø og Sjælland.
Omgivelserne er perfekte til at tage en tur, vandre eller bare slappe af ved stranden med en god bog. Du kan finde flere oplysninger ved tryk på i.

translations.name: notice
translations.content:
Korshavn Lystbådebro liegt bei Fyns Hoved - einem der schönsten Orte Dänemarks - und gehört dem Segelklub Odense.
An der Brücke finden Sie Strom und Wasser sowie die Möglichkeit Ihren Müll zu entsorgen. Öffentliche Toiletten - ohne Dusche - sind nur 250 Meter von der Brücke entfernt. Die Umgebung ist unglaublich malerisch mit hohen Hängen, flachen Bereichen und einem atemberaubenden Blick auf Æbelø, Jütland, Samsø und Seeland.
Die Umgebung eignet sich perfekt für Spaziergänge, Wanderungen oder einfach nur zum Entspannen am Strand mit einem guten Buch. Für weitere Informationen drücken Sie i.

Harba sticker can be picked up at the harboroffice, Nørregade 1A, and put so it is visible from the bridge. You only need one sticker in all harbors using Harba, it is free and required in some harbors. When you have placed the sticker on your boat you can type the ID in the "Harba ID" field under edit boat, then the harbormaster has a easier time determining, when you have payed.

translations.name: notice
translations.content:
The harbor, which is owned by the self-governing institution "Stige Ø Marina" and is administered by Odense Sailing Club, is located inwards in the canal on the port side, approx. 1/2 mile before you meet Odin's Bridge. The port is a member of the Freeport Scheme. 
Toilets with showers are located at the back of the club's red clubhouse.
Unfortunately, there is no public transport to Odense city center from the port, but if you have bicycles with you, you can cycle off several roads to the city center. The nearest shopping opportunity is Rema 1000 on the corner of Skibhusvej and Sandhusvej. Further out on the island you will find the former landfill for Odense Municipality, which has now been transformed into a beautiful and attractive green recreation area in very hilly terrain, with ice cream parlor, playground and other activity equipment.

translations.name: notice
translations.content:
Havnen, som ejes af den selvejende institution "Stige Ø Lystbådehavn" og administreres af Odense Sejlklub, ligger for indadgående i kanalen på bagbord side, ca. 1/2 sømil før du møder Odins Bro. Havnen er medlem af Frihavnsordningen. Toiletter med bad findes bag på klubbens røde klubhus.
Der er desværre ikke offentlig transport til Odense centrum fra havnen, men har man cykler med, kan man cykle af flere veje til byens centrum. Nærmeste handlemulighed er Rema 1000 på hjørnet af Skibhusvej og Sandhusvej. Længere ude på øen finder du den tidligere losseplads for Odense Kommune, som nu er omdannet til et flot og attraktivt grønt rekreationsområde i meget kuperet terræn, med iskiosk, legeplads og andet aktivitetsudstyr.

translations.name: notice
translations.content:
Der Hafen, der der Selbstverwaltungsinstitution "Stige Ø Marina" gehört und vom Odense Sailing Club verwaltet wird, liegt im Kanal einwärts auf der Backbordseite, ca. 1/2 Meile bevor Sie Odins Brücke treffen. Der Hafen ist Mitglied des Freeport Scheme. Toiletten mit Duschen befinden sich hinter dem roten Clubhaus des Clubs.
Leider gibt es vom Hafen aus keine öffentlichen Verkehrsmittel in die Innenstadt von Odense, aber wenn Sie Fahrräder dabei haben, können Sie über mehrere Straßen in die Innenstadt radeln. Die nächste Einkaufsmöglichkeit ist Rema 1000 an der Ecke Skibhusvej und Sandhusvej. Weiter draußen auf der Insel finden Sie die ehemalige Deponie der Gemeinde Odense, die jetzt in ein schönes und attraktives grünes Erholungsgebiet in sehr hügeligem Gelände mit Eisdiele, Spielplatz und anderen Aktivitätsgeräten umgewandelt wurde.
